From: Steffen Trumtrar <s.trumtrar@pengutronix.de>
Date: Mon, 6 Jul 2020 14:58:37 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] dt-bindings: Add DS2482 as trivial device

The Maxim DS2482 is an I2C to 1-wire bridge.

Signed-off-by: Steffen Trumtrar <s.trumtrar@pengutronix.de>
---
 Documentation/devicetree/bindings/trivial-devices.yaml | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/trivial-devices.yaml b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/trivial-devices.yaml
index 550a2e5c9e05..f6a27c78573e 100644
--- a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/trivial-devices.yaml
+++ b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/trivial-devices.yaml
@@ -169,6 +169,8 @@ properties:
           - maxim,ds1803-100
             # 10 kOhm digital potentiometer with I2C interface
           - maxim,ds3502
+            # 10-bit 8 channels 300ks/s SPI ADC with temperature sensor
+          - maxim,ds2482
             # Low-Power, 4-/12-Channel, 2-Wire Serial, 12-Bit ADCs
           - maxim,max1237
             # Temperature Sensor, I2C interface
